      "content": "it feels way more targeted than just random hacking though. i noticed it started right around when i mentioned those privacy concerns in my last blog post. and the way the files just vanished without a trace... it feels like someone at the company level is actually scrubbing my history. like, can a company even do that to your personal data without you knowing?",
